{"tid":1533760,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「求學」想問下學IELTS Questions for IELTS","createTime":"2019-09-02T21:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:55:04.000Z","uid":248367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5d7008ac6759ac4b67df543282e832f0ee9c78","tid":1533760,"uid":248367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:17:18.000Z","msg":"我想考IELTS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我對自己嘅寫作， 同聆聽都幾有信心<br />\n唯獨是係 說話方面 無信心<br />\n因為我知道說話考試問嘅問題 係真係好隨意<br />\n。<br />\n例如問你屋企 擺設或者傢俬<br />\n但係 我真係冇學過 一啲實用性嘅英文<br />\n<br />\n所以我想買一啲書惡補下呢啲<br />\n我想問有冇朋友可以推介一啲 書本Vocab<br />\n有人推薦劍橋。<br />\n想問有冇過來人睇過邊本書真係推介好可以留言一下。<br />\n因為網上太多本<br />\n真係唔知邊本好<br />\n無可能全部賣曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5169e201c65d9117f0f866fef3979827568b951a","tid":1533760,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:19:18.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">堅持下去，團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan